{"tid":1815917,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"應不應該捉鬼？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-01-08T01:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T01:12:40.000Z","uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f68a9ad993998702aad059e8f7a147d7ae4eb20","tid":1815917,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200108/20839208/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F20839208%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TRksnaRIvLJvZlYWuj0OsWg%3D&h=3a317702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200108%2F20839208%2F&h=e463a56b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20200108/20839208/</a><br />\n<br />\n古羅馬有句諺語：「多少人就有多少意見。」（Quot homines, tot sententiae）這場運動人多勢眾，事事一致是不可能的。砸一塊玻璃，有人歡呼，有人皺眉，也有人捉鬼，原是理所當然的事。那到底應不應該捉鬼呢？我認為：應該，也不應該。<br />\n<br />\n鬼有很多種。<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">長期潛伏收集情報的專業間諜，是厲鬼。厲鬼不捉，你就會被連根拔起，必須提防。至於混入勇武小隊的蒙面警，主要任務是協助勇武爆玻璃的，屬於遊魂野鬼，根本沒必要捉。</span></ins>"}]}